Burnbright changes:
 * Registrations / events now only persist to DB on final purchase / book, so there are no unnecessary DB entries.
 * Summary page with modify option
 * Modularised code a bit more
 * Added various hooks for extending
 * Renamed classes to be more readable (eg: RSVP becomes EventRegistration)
 * Allow extended classes to use custom templates eg: MyEvent_recieptEmail.ss
 * Put less reliance on template files (eg: no need for Event.ss)
 * Pruned alot of unused code & features that don't work